title: WATCH: Babes and Cassper bring all the moves in new music video - Times LIVE
text:
In memes: Twitter loses its mind over 'Justin Bieber Wololo remix' 
The pair finally released the highly-anticipated music video for their hit collaboration Family and, well, it was worth the wait. 
The video followed the pair as they drove to a spot in Lamontville, Durban to have a dance-off. 
Both Cassper and Babes are known for their incredible dance moves and their talent was on full display in the video. 
Just take a look at some of their moves.
